data.eO_DESCRIPTION: IS4Q2500057 - WARDROBES AND PARTITIONS - INSTALLATION OF A BUMPER TO PREVENT DAMAGE TO THE SWITCHES ON THE WING BULKHEAD ASSEMBLY

data.contenT_DESCRIPTION:
Aircraft Affected:
Service Bulletin: DHC ---8 Aircraft Models 401 and 402 Serial Numbers 4001,
4003 thru 4078.
Production: ModSum 4 ---154672 will be incorporated before delivery on
applicable DHC ---8 Aircraft Model 401 and 402 Serial Number
4079 and subsequent.
Verification: ModSum 4 ---154672 has been incorporated on DHC ---8
Aircraft Model 402 Serial Number 4018.
